INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2011-04-07 16:29:25','2011-04-07 16:29:25','One month into the launch of Etiquette Clothiers - on Vogue.com with our dear friend Waris. Waris Ahluwalia tells of his \"5 Summer Essentials.\"\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/vogue_111111.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-238\" title=\"vogue_111111\" src=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/vogue_111111.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"515\" height=\"351\" /></a>Waris Ahluwalia, www.houseofwaris.com #craftsmanship #artisanship  - is that how you blog? #etiquetteofblogging','en Vogue','Etiquette Clothiers Launches Globally, April 2011','publish','open','open','','vogu','','','2011-12-14 21:18:10','2011-12-14 21:18:10','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/?p=1',0,'post','',0),(2,1,'2011-10-07 16:29:25','2011-10-07 16:29:25','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2011-10-07 16:29:25','2011-10-07 16:29:25','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(5,1,'2012-02-16 22:58:30','2012-02-16 22:58:30','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>ETIQUETTE + JONNY DETIGER:</strong></em>\r\nIntroducing an exclusive collection of limited-edition luxury garments.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In a commitment to elevating the undergarment, Etiquette Clothiers, in collaboration with Dutch artist and designer, <a title=\"Jonny Detiger\" href=\"http://www.jonnydetiger.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Jonny Detiger</a>, presents an exclusive collection of socks and underwear.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!--more-->NY-based Dutch artist and designer, Jonny Detiger, partners with Etiquette Clothiers , to launch a collection of socks and underwear for Men, Women, and Kids. The design represents an aligned vision: transcend the mundane, celebrate life, and joyfully bridge the gap between the everyday and the exceptional. A visual exploration, the theme of “Positive/Negative Spaces” celebrates the interplay between dreams and reality, expressed in the contrasting blue and white colors of signature classic Dutch Delft style.</p>\r\n&nbsp;','Jonny Detiger','Excerpt for Special Edition Test Post','publish','open','closed','','jonny-detiger','','','2012-02-21 15:26:03','2012-02-21 15:26:03','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/?post_type=specialedition&#038;p=5',0,'specialedition','',0),(7,1,'2011-11-16 23:00:22','2011-11-16 23:00:22','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>ETIQUETTE + J.P. GRAYTOK</strong></em>:\r\nIntroducing the \"Ultimate Sock Garter\"</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a title=\"J.P. Graytok\" href=\"http://www.collarcompany.com/home.php\" target=\"_blank\">J.P. Graytok</a>, a purveyor of exclusive men’s haberdashery and accessories for luxury department stores since 1979 partners partnered with Etiquette Clothiers to unite old-school sensibilities with new-school attitude and modern design.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!--more-->The sock garter is a wardrobe wonder that masterfully prevents socks from slipping down. An often-overlooked accoutrement—once found beneath the ensemble of distinguished gentlemen everywhere—it revives a time-honored tradition and keeps a classic alive.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Basics of Etiquette: \"A man should keep his drinks down, and his socks up.”</p>','J.P. Graytok','','publish','open','open','','graytok','','','2012-02-21 16:38:32','2012-02-21 16:38:32','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/?post_type=specialedition&#038;p=7',0,'specialedition','',0),(8,1,'2012-02-21 16:39:37','2012-02-21 16:39:37','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>ETIQUETTE + J.P. GRAYTOK</strong></em>:\nIntroducing the \"Ultimate Sock Garter\"</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a title=\"J.P. Graytok\" href=\"http://www.collarcompany.com/home.php\" target=\"_blank\">J.P. Graytok</a>, a purveyor of exclusive men’s haberdashery and accessories for luxury department stores since 1979 partners partnered with Etiquette Clothiers to unite old-school sensibilities with new-school attitude and modern design.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!--more-->The sock garter is a wardrobe wonder that masterfully prevents socks from slipping down. An often-overlooked accoutrement—once found beneath the ensemble of distinguished gentlemen everywhere—it revives a time-honored tradition and keeps a classic alive.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Basics of Etiquette: \"A man should keep his drinks down, and his socks up.”</p>','J.P. Graytok','','inherit','open','open','','7-autosave','','','2012-02-21 16:39:37','2012-02-21 16:39:37','',7,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/?p=8',0,'revision','',0),(9,1,'2011-10-07 16:29:25','2011-10-07 16:29:25','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','inher