/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/DCANDY_INSER.tif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-246\" title=\"Daily Candy\" src=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/DCANDY_INSER.tif\" alt=\"\" /></a>\r\n\r\n\"Mama owns her baby weight in Jimmy Choos, so it’s no surprise baby’s sock drawer is bursting at the seams. Clear out another: Etiquette Clothiers, a company dedicated to perfecting dressing basics like socks, is coming to town. The line includes well-considered underthings and footwear for grown-ups, but it’s the baby socks that have us smiling from ankle dimples to toes.\"   Read the rest of the feature on Daily Candy Kids New York Edition, December 12, 2011.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Products Featured:</strong> Happy Boy Bundle -sku# ywsg11-01\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Daily Candy Kids','Daily Candy Kids discovered the Etiquette Clothiers Baby Bundle this week #properpampering','inherit','open','open','','231-revision-9','','','2011-12-14 21:27:48','2011-12-14 21:27:48','',231,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/2011/12/231-revision-9/',0,'revision','',0),(34,1,'2011-11-18 20:28:45','2011-11-18 20:28:45','','2','','inherit','open','open','','2','','','2011-11-18 20:28:45','2011-11-18 20:28:45','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(35,1,'2011-11-18 20:28:48','2011-11-18 20:28:48','','3','','inherit','open','open','','3','','','2011-11-18 20:28:48','2011-11-18 20:28:48','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(36,1,'2012-02-17 20:34:43','2012-02-17 20:34:43','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>ETIQUETTE + GLOBE-TROTTER:</strong></em>\r\nIntroducing the “Etiquette Koi Clouds” Limited Edition Series</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A bespoke collection of travel cases and trolleys by Etiquette Clothiers in collaboration with <a title=\"Globetrotter\" href=\"http://www.globetrotter1897.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Globe-Trotter</a>,  the British maker of luxury luggage since 1897.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!--more--></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Made in England of signature “Vulcan Fibre” and skillfully constructed by hand, from start to finish, Globe-Trotter stands for heritage and craftsmanship. The brand’s tradition of quality – and charming personality – are unique hallmarks of these timeless style icons.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The series is customized with Etiquette design and details, including a fabric lining in the signature Japanese-inspired “Koi Clouds” pattern.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>','Globe Trotter 1897','','publish','open','closed','','gallery-test-post','','','2012-02-21 15:21:33','2012-02-21 15:21:33','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/?post_type=specialedition&#038;p=36',0,'specialedition','',0),(33,1,'2011-11-18 20:28:42','2011-11-18 20:28:42','','1','','inherit','open','open','','1','','','2011-11-18 20:28:42','2011-11-18 20:28:42','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(311,1,'2012-02-09 19:42:34','2012-02-09 19:42:34','','gt4','','inherit','open','open','','gt4','','','2012-02-09 19:42:34','2012-02-09 19:42:34','',36,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/gt4.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(40,1,'2012-02-21 15:21:19','2012-02-21 15:21:19','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>ETIQUETTE + GLOBE-TROTTER:</strong></em>\nIntroducing the “Koi Clouds” Limited Edition Series</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A bespoke collection of travel cases and trolleys by Etiquette Clothiers in collaboration with <a title=\"Globetrotter\" href=\"http://www.globetrotter1897.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Globe-Trotter</a>,  the British maker of luxury luggage since 1897.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!--more--></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Made in England of signature “Vulcan Fibre” and skillfully constructed by hand, from start to finish, Globe-Trotter stands for heritage and craftsmanship. The brand’s tradition of quality – and charming personality – are unique hallmarks of these timeless style icons.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The series is customized with Etiquette design and details, including a fabric lining in the signature Japanese-inspired “Koi Clouds” pattern.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>','Globe Trotter 1897','','inherit','open','open','','36-autosave','','','2012-02-21 15:21:19','2012-02-21 15:21:19','',36,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/2011/11/36-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(41,1,'2011-11-18 20:38:11','2011-11-18 20:38:11','','globe-trotter','','inherit','open','open','','globe-trotter','','','2011-11-18 20:38:11','2011-11-18 20:38:11','',36,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/globe-trotter.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(66,1,'2011-12-09 23:48:01','2011-12-09 23:48:01','','2','','inherit','open','open','','gt2','','','2011-12-09 23:48:01','2011-12-09 23:48:01','',36,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/gt2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(278,1,'2012-02-09 16:50:11','2012-02-09 16:50:11','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/BNB1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-279\" title=\"BNB1\" src=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/BNB1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"349\" /></a>We would like to thank everyone who stopped by our booth at Bread &amp; Butter Berlin and making it a successful show. It was great catching up with clients, friends and building new relationships.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/BNB2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-280\" title=\"BNB2\" src=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/BNB2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"258\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/BNB3.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-281\" title=\"BNB3\" src=\"http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/BNB3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"531\" height=\"270\" /></a>','Etiquette @ Bread & Butter 2012','','publish','open','open','','etiquette-bread-and-butter-l-o-c-k-berlin-2012','','','2012-02-10 21:08:14','2012-02-10 21:08:14','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/?p=278',0,'post','',0),(69,1,'2012-02-21 15:25:42','2012-02-21 15:25:42','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>ETIQUETTE + JONNY DETIGER:</strong></em>\nIntroducing an exclusive collection of limited-edition, luxury garments.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In a commitment to elevating the undergarment, Etiquette Clothiers, in collaboration with Dutch artist and designer, <a title=\"Jonny Detiger\" href=\"http://www.jonnydetiger.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Jonny Detiger</a>, presents an exclusive collection.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!--more-->NY-based Dutch artist and designer, Jonny Detiger, partners with Etiquette Clothiers , to launch a collection of socks and underwear for Men, Women, and Kids. The design represents an aligned vision: transcend the mundane, celebrate life, and joyfully bridge the gap between the everyday and the exceptional. A visual exploration, the theme of “Positive/Negative Spaces” celebrates the interplay between dreams and reality, expressed in the contrasting blue and white colors of signature classic Dutch Delft style.</p>\n&nbsp;','Jonny Detiger','Excerpt for Special Edition Test Post','inherit','open','open','','5-autosave','','','2012-02-21 15:25:42','2012-02-21 15:25:42','',5,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/2011/12/5-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(74,1,'2011-12-12 15:12:22','2011-12-12 15:12:22','','abicilogo','','inherit','open','open','','abicilogo','','','2011-12-12 15:12:22','2011-12-12 15:12:22','',73,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/abicilogo.gif',1,'attachment','image/gif',0),(73,1,'2011-12-12 15:24:24','2011-12-12 15:24:24','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> <em><strong>ETIQUETTE + ABICI:</strong></em>\r\nIntroducing our Limited Edition Velocino Bicycle.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Etiquette Clothiers in exclusive collaboration with Italian manufacturer, <a title=\"Abici\" href=\"http://www.abici-italia.it\" target=\"_blank\">Abici</a>, launches the limited edition Velocino bicycle, a charming re-make of a city cycle dating back to the early 1950s.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!--more--> Based on the classic model, the re-make showcases the excellence in design and manufacturing of Abici, with added design and detail by Etiquette to include a Brooks Saddle, Brooks leather tool bag, and handmade black leather handles.  Portable, light and handy, this model is a perfect size for city cycling.</p>','Abici Italia','','publish','open','open','','73','','','2012-02-21 15:24:28','2012-02-21 15:24:28','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/?post_type=specialedition&#038;p=73',0,'specialedition','',0),(350,3,'2012-02-17 23:14:49','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2012-02-17 23:14:49','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/?p=350',0,'post','',0),(343,1,'2012-02-10 21:01:20','2012-02-10 21:01:20','','laund_logo','','inherit','open','open','','laund_logo','','','2012-02-10 21:01:20','2012-02-10 21:01:20','',82,'http://etiquette.swedenunlimited.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/laund_logo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(48,1,'2011-12-08 21:15:57','2011-12-08 21:15:57','Hey here\'s some stuff about socks.\n\n<a hre